    "Id": "chassisdef_capra_CP-J22",
    "Name": "Capra",
    "Details": "The CP-J22 is a thorough 3058 modernization of the Capra concept, replacing all original weapons with ER Small Lasers, Small Pulse Lasers and a pair of ER Medium Lasers for meaningful reach improvement over prior variants. Ferro-Fibrous armor and double heat sinks address the original's two biggest shortcomings, giving the chassis noticeably better staying power in the close-range engagements it was always designed to win.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Nimble</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 0.99</color></b>",
